lead_paragraph: West Bromwich Albion missed a chance to move into the Premier League's top six when they were held to a 0-0 draw by Middlesbrough on Sunday despite making the better opportunities in a dull game.

headline.print_headline: West Brom Miss Chance of Top-Six Spot
